INSPIRATION AND PRIOR WORK

ReKey is a full rewrite inspired by PassCore, originally developed by Unosquare LLC:

  PassCore — https://github.com/unosquare/passcore
  Copyright (c) 2016-2022 Unosquare LLC
  Licensed under the MIT License

PassCore provided the original concept of a self-service Active Directory
password change portal. ReKey rebuilds the idea from scratch on modern
foundations (.NET 10 LTS, React 19, MUI 6) while adding email notifications,
password expiry reminders, HaveIBeenPwned integration, reCAPTCHA v3,
hardened security headers, and a clean contemporary UI.

